<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ei Hukhingpa chuh zuiin,
 Kipahna la sa'ng ie -
 Zatam chung chuong tahen,
 Ei khawtuohna'n A luong tuok in,
 Thisan in ei chaw'i-
 A min chuh lopipen hen.

[V2]
 &quot;Hallelujah, kumsawt Lalpa,
 Lopipen hen,&quot; tih hi;
 Ka kumsawt la chu ahi,
 Ei Hukhingpa, ei hung Tanpa;
 Migilo Tanpa lopipen hen,
 Ei khawtuohna'n A luong tuok in;
 Ka hinna'n A thi'i-
 A min chuh lopipen hen.

[V3]
 2. Thim nuoi leh hatlohna ah,
 A vanglien ka belh;
 Sing-zatam chungchuong ta hen;
 Sietlei dogal tam lak ah,
 Lau lo a ei pui zing,
 A min chuh lopipen hen.

[V4]
 3. Ka kawm a vak in, ei veng,
 In ei luongmuon hi;
 A min chuh lopipen hen,
 Jordan lui ei pui kaiin;
 Van gam ei tun ina,
 Amin chuh lopipen hen.</lyrics>
<title>I WILL SING HIS PRAISES</title>
</song>